.TH PROGRAMMINGHABITS 1 "November 2025" "1.0.0" "User Manual"
.SH NAME
programminghabits \- Productivity timer with health breaks for Linux
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B programminghabits
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B programminghabits
is a Python-based utility designed to integrate the Pomodoro technique into your workflow while enforcing healthy habits during breaks
.PP
It provides a system tray icon to manage the timer. When the work timer expires, a full-screen overlay appears, reminding the user to take a break, stretch, look away from the screen, or drink water.
.PP
It automatically pauses media players (Spotify, YouTube, etc.) via DBus during breaks.
.SH CONFIGURATION
Configuration is stored in \fB~/.config/programminghabits/config.json\fR. You can also edit settings via the GUI by clicking the system tray icon.
